    {
      "id": "1bdac24f-bafb-451e-bb6d-ed295ccfb4cb",
      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $A$ un anneau commutatif et $I$ un id{\\'e}al de $A$.\n\nOn note $\\sqrt{I} = \\{ x \\in A \\text{ tq } \\exists\\ n \\in \\N \\text{ tq } x^n \\in I \\}$\n(radical de $I$).",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(A\\)</span> un anneau commutatif et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(I\\)</span> un id<span>é</span>al de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(A\\)</span>.</p>\n<p>On note <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sqrt{I} = \\{ x \\in A \\text{ tq } \\exists\\ n \\in \\N \\text{ tq } x^n \\in I \\}\\)</span> (radical de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(I\\)</span>).</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "70942ab9-23aa-48fd-899a-cc0ad7bef78c",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que $\\sqrt{I}$ est un id{\\'e}al de $A$.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sqrt{I}\\)</span> est un id<span>é</span>al de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(A\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "232d5e30-ff35-47a1-a752-56579c6d5a48",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que $\\sqrt{\\sqrt I} = \\sqrt I$.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sqrt{\\sqrt I} = \\sqrt I\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "e8af0de5-b66d-4da4-baaf-3541f4fe4b00",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que $\\sqrt{I \\cap J} = \\sqrt I \\cap \\sqrt J$ et\n    $\\sqrt{I + J} \\supset \\sqrt I + \\sqrt J$.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sqrt{I \\cap J} = \\sqrt I \\cap \\sqrt J\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sqrt{I + J} \\supset \\sqrt I + \\sqrt J\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "7904c86d-0b7b-46b8-a990-0058402f6526",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Exemple : $A = \\Z$, $I = 3648\\Z$. Trouver $\\sqrt I$.",
        "html": "<p>Exemple : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(A = \\Z\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(I = 3648\\Z\\)</span>. Trouver <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sqrt I\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "a09b8fc3-e329-4dda-865b-621651c25078",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Remarque : la r{\\'e}ciproque fausse : $A = \\Z[X]$, $I=(X)$, $J=(X+4)$.\n$114\\Z$.",
        "html": "<p>Remarque : la r<span>é</span>ciproque fausse : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(A = \\Z[X]\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(I=(X)\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(J=(X+4)\\)</span>. <span class=\"math inline\">\\(114\\Z\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
